Information.ShortDescription: Steps from local shopping and dining and offering a top-end style complete with available views of the Manhattan skyline, apartments at Madox are redefining what it means to have an apartment in Jersey.
Information.LongDescription: Leave the office behind and find yourself in a neighborhood not of glass and steel but of bricks and trees and people. The is Paulus Hook. And with the arrival of Madox, this community on the Hudson finally has an apartment that fits the spirit of the neighborhood.

The Crest at Fort Lee Apartments in Fort Lee, NJ has 1, 2 and 3 bedroom apartments and 1 and 2 bedroom lofts for rent. These Fort Lee apartments are in a gated apartment community that provides modest seclusion and convenience to all major highways in New Jersey and New York City as well as the NJ Transit. With the great location in Fort Lee, NJ, the city will be at your fingertips with mountain views, upgraded apartment units and amazing amenities, including a free coffee bar and Cyber Lounge, private heated pool with tanning deck,indoor basketball, 24-hour fitness center andbusiness center. The Crest at Fort Lee Apartments come with a full-size washer and dryer, private balcony and spacious walk-in closets. The upgraded apartments include granite counter tops, ceramic tile flooring, two-tone paint and brushed nickel hardware accents.
Our residents tell us they live at The Crest at Fort Lee Apartments in Fort Lee, NJ because:
Superb customer service 24-hour emergency maintenance The best kept secret in Fort Lee, NJ with beautiful bright big apartment floor plans Private garages available Granite countertops and designer upgrades available In New York City at a moments notice On the NJ Transit Bus Line and convenient to highways Walking distance to grocery stores, restaurants and banks 24-Hour Fitness Center The grass is really greener on the Crest side and magnificent mountain views
The Crest at Fort Lee Apartments is a recipient of the CEL & Associates A List Award for Customer Service --

Information.ShortDescription: Apartments At White Flint! Great for people on the go! Beautiful apartments. Ideal location. Strathmore Court is one of the most alluring communities in the North Bethesda region.
Information.LongDescription: Strathmore Court is the perfect home for people who are constantly on the go. Less than one block from the White Flint Metro Station, this unique community is only a short distance from all of the fashion, food and entertainment available from Bethesda to Rockville. Strathmore Court offers convenient access via the Metro to the entire metropolitan area. A variety of floor plans offer affordable, comfortable luxury in one- and two-bedroom apartments with sunrooms, balconies or patios. A decorative brick facade, with attractive architectural detailing, adds charm to this distinctive, mid-rise apartment community with high-rise amenities. Residents can stroll through a park-like courtyard accented by large trees and beautiful landscaping. Free underground parking provides convenience and peace of mind.

Information.ShortDescription: The luxury apartments you want, in just the right location.
Information.LongDescription: Set in the heart of downtown Bethesda comes the uptown elegance of The Metropolitan. These superb apartment homes are smartly designed to enhance your life with a level of comfort you may never have experienced. Spacious and open, filled with contemporary features and finished to perfection, enriched by an inspiring complement of amenities and situated just steps away from an array of dynamic destinations, The Metropolitan at Bethesda brings you the best of everything.

Information.ShortDescription: Spacious town home rentals with private entrances Within walking distance of the Grosvenor-Strathmore Metro (red line) Quaint, secluded community in a quiet, wooded setting
Information.LongDescription: Timberlawn is a townhome community! You are glad to be home at Timberlawn Crescent. This cozy environment is excellent for those looking for an easier drive to work or who want to take advantage of the public transportation system. Timberlawn Crescent continues to provide a community atmosphere, as well as convenience to nearby shopping and recreation. You'll appreciate the spacious floor plans which also have additional storage provided. Located in a quiet area of North Bethesda, Timberlawn Crescent is surrounded by jogging paths and playgrounds, but residents are always within an arm's reach of wonderful dining and shopping destinations. Enjoy life here with us!
